        <h1>Orange King's Stick Mod</h1>
        <p>Welcome to the official page for the Orange King's Stick Mod for Minecraft!</p>
        <h2>Abilities:</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Massive Damage:</strong> Deals powerful damage to enemies.</li>
            <li><strong>Knockback:</strong> Sends enemies flying upon impact.</li>
            <li><strong>Slowness Effect:</strong> Slows enemies after being hit.</li>
            <li><strong>Minion Summon:</strong> Summons minions to fight alongside you.</li>
            <li><strong>Ground Smash:</strong> Creates a shockwave that knocks back enemies.</li>
            <li><strong>Flight:</strong> Temporarily grants the player flight.</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>How to Install:</h2>
        <p>To install the Orange King's Stick Mod, follow these steps:</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Download the mod <a href="https://github.com/yourusername/OrangeKingsStickMod/releases" target="_blank">here</a>.</li>
            <li>Place the .jar file in the 'mods' folder of your Minecraft directory.</li>
            <li>Launch Minecraft with the Forge mod loader.</li>
        </ol>
        <h2>GitHub Repository</h2>
        <p>For more information and the latest updates, visit the repository on GitHub:</p>
        <a href="https://github.com/yourusername/OrangeKingsStickMod" target="_blank">Orange King's Stick Mod Repository</a>
